node.text: We've been waiting for this one, turn it up 🔊 Marvel Studios' @ShangChi and the Legend of the Ten Rings is in theaters September 3. Get tickets now at the link in bio.

node.text: Marvel Studios' #Eternals have arrived. Take a look at an @EntertainmentWeekly exclusive photo from the film and experience it in theaters November 5.
Here are the new @EntertainmentWeekly exclusive covers featuring Marvel Studios' @Eternals. Experience it in theaters November 5. Read the full story on EW.com.
